    "Description": {
      "type": "text",
      "dtype": "String",
      "label": "Metapower Description",
      "value": "<p align=\"center\"><em><span lang=\"en-us\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">Embarking upon the inaugural tier of Telepathy, Manipulators unlock the capacity to plumb the innermost recesses of another's thoughts. Initiating this feat entails directing one's focus upon a living being perceptible through their senses or by any psychic means. Once engaged, the phenomenon of Mind Reading grants the Manipulator insight into their own mental contemplations in tandem with those of the subject for several minutes. As mastery deepens, adept telepaths can extend this link to encompass multiple minds or bridge greater distances. Exceptionally skilled practitioners might exploit cunning queries to navigate their subjects' thoughts, uncovering concealed truths or subtle correlations hidden beneath the surface. Beware, however, for a misstep in activation may cloud the Manipulator's own thoughts in a nebulous haze for a transient duration.</span></em></p>"
